      <div>
        <a
          href="https://yandex.ru/maps?whatshere%5Bpoint%5D=37.668904%2C55.774561&whatshere%5Bzoom%5D=18.819712&ll=37.669085762467624%2C55.77426729014845&z=18.819712&si=r7j7h7y8fjzvh7vpk1ybn5npj8"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
          class="mt-5 flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1 p-3 text-indigo-700 hover:underline dark:text-amber-400"
        >
          <p class="text-xs md:text-base lg:text-lg">
            Нижняя Красносельская улица, 40/12к2
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="mt-5 w-full">
      <summary class="text-center">Как до кас добраться?</summary>
